<!-- What is Programming? -->
Programming is an practice that boost our logical thinking and improves a problem-solving skill. Programming is the mental process of thinking instructions to give to a machine.

<!-- What is python? -->
Python is an interpreted, object-oriented, high-level programming language with dynamic semantics. Python supports modules and packages, which encourages program modularity and code reuse. Python is designed to be easy to learn and it is highly portable and extensible programming language.